
==Bio==

" I’m the co-founder of Blue Link Labs, the team behind [https://beakerbrowser.com/ Beaker], a peer-to-peer Web browser, and Hashbase, a cloud peer service for files hosted with the [https://datproject.org/ Dat protocol].

Before starting Blue Link Labs, I worked at Cloudflare, where I helped build their Apps platform, and before that I spent time at the [https://www.recurse.com/ Recurse Center], an amazing community for programmers.

I grew up in rural northern Michigan, but I currently reside in Austin, TX.

I’m passionate about re-decentralizing the Web."
(https://taravancil.com/about/)

